---
title: Creamy Cheddar Cheeseburgers with Seasoned Potato Wedges & Special Sauce
description: Cheeseburgers are pretty much a perfect food. Beef patty, a slice of cheese, maybe a squeeze of ketchup—that’s all you need for a good one. For a GREAT one, however, it’s best to leave it to the pros (aka our chefs) who settle for nothing less. Here, pimento-style cheese (aka cheese in its most flavorful, spreadable form) is dolloped onto juicy beef patties and melted to perfection. The cheesy patties are then sandwiched between toasty, buttery buns along with charred onion, tomato, and pickles. Oh, and did we mention there’s oven fries and special sauce on the side for dipping? Goodbye, just-plain-good burgers!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-cheddar-cheeseburgers-2b618d5d.jpg
